---
import PageLayout2 from "../layouts/PageLayout2.astro";
const pageTitle = "Work with us";
const pageDescription =
  "Learn how your brand can reach thousands of enthousiast travel lovers.";
---

<PageLayout2 pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2
        class="text-5xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-slate-800 sm:text-6xl pt-12 pb-4"
      >
        {pageTitle}
      </h2>
      <p class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-2xl text-gray-500 pb-4">
        {pageDescription}
      </p>
      <div
        class="bg-teal-800 p-5 rounded-md text-white font-medium text-2xl mb-5 inline-block mx-auto"
      >
        Send us a DM on <a
          href="https://instagram.com/findajourney"
          class="underline">Instagram</a
        > to work togheter.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-lg lg:text-xl">
      <p>
        As the travel industry continues to evolve, travel brands must find
        innovative ways to reach their target audience and drive business
        growth. In today's digital age, social media and travel blogs have
        become essential tools for building brand awareness and engaging with
        potential customers. That's why partnering with our travel Instagram
        page and blog is a smart move for any travel brand looking to increase
        their online presence and expand their reach.
      </p>

      <p>
        Firstly, our travel Instagram page and blog are dedicated to sharing
        compelling travel content with our followers. We have built a strong and
        engaged community of travel enthusiasts who trust our recommendations
        and are eager to discover new destinations, experiences, and products.
        By partnering with us, travel brands can tap into this community and
        reach a highly targeted audience of travelers who are actively seeking
        inspiration and information about travel.
      </p>

      <p>
        Secondly, our travel Instagram page and blog offer a range of
        partnership opportunities that can be tailored to meet the unique needs
        of different travel brands. We can create custom content, such as
        sponsored posts, product reviews, or destination guides, that align with
        the brand's messaging and marketing objectives. We also offer social
        media takeovers, giveaways, and other engagement activities that can
        help travel brands connect with our followers and build brand loyalty.
      </p>

      <p>
        Lastly, our travel Instagram page and blog are run by a team of
        experienced travel writers and photographers who have a deep
        understanding of the travel industry and the needs of today's travelers.
        This means that travel brands can be assured of high-quality content
        that resonates with their target audience and accurately reflects their
        brand values and messaging.
      </p>

      <p>
        In conclusion, partnering with our travel Instagram page and blog is a
        smart move for any travel brand looking to build brand awareness, engage
        with potential customers, and drive business growth. With our dedicated
        following, broad reach, tailored partnership opportunities, and
        experienced team, we can help travel brands achieve their marketing
        objectives and reach a highly targeted audience of travel enthusiasts.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-teal-800 my-5 rounded-md">
      <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 sm:py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-10"
      >
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl">
            Statistics
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xl text-teal-200 sm:mt-4">
            Our targetted audience loves to travel and is ready to book with
            you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <dl
          class="mt-10 text-center sm:max-w-3xl sm:mx-auto sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-8"
        >
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt
              class="order-2 mt-2 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-teal-200"
            >
              Followers
            </dt>
            <dd class="order-1 text-5xl font-extrabold text-white">4k</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col mt-10 sm:mt-0">
            <dt
              class="order-2 mt-2 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-teal-200"
            >
              Likes / post
            </dt>
            <dd class="order-1 text-5xl font-extrabold text-white">350</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col mt-10 sm:mt-0">
            <dt
              class="order-2 mt-2 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-teal-200"
            >
              Engagement rate
            </dt>
            <dd class="order-1 text-5xl font-extrabold text-white">8%</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout2>
